MidPoint 4.8.6 "Curie" Update 7
-------------------------------

Release 4.8.7 is a sixty-fourth midPoint release code-named Curie.
The 4.8.7 release brings security, stability and miscellaneous bugfixes.

Release date: 18th March 2025
Release type: Long-term support release (LTS)
End of support: 17th October 2028

Please see the release notes for detailed list of changes:
https://docs.evolveum.com/midpoint/release/4.8.7/
